* fix(release): link commit hashes in fallback release notes ([`fdc6e90`](https://github.com/oomol-lab/LockIME/commit/fdc6e9072a5938142f76ad367e414d8433263f3e))
* feat: add Homebrew install via custom tap cask ([`fcd6e6c`](https://github.com/oomol-lab/LockIME/commit/fcd6e6cbbf08dd39ddfdc061486215bffbfe3adc))
* ci(release): always list direct-push commits in release notes ([`1ac2d8b`](https://github.com/oomol-lab/LockIME/commit/1ac2d8bb8e66866f476503f0effc7e77af667761))
* docs(readme): center the title and add the app icon ([`a2388fd`](https://github.com/oomol-lab/LockIME/commit/a2388fd2370ebd01673e1f416b3fc697a2f353b6))

## New Contributors
* @BlackHole1 made their first contribution in https://github.com/oomol-lab/LockIME/pull/2

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/oomol-lab/LockIME/compare/v1.1.0...v1.1.1
]]></description>
